item.description: Lora Stone is a Sai Shakti Healer and Teacher of the Ancient Indian Divine Knowledge. She lived and studied in Penukonda, South India, for over a decade under the direct guidance of Avatar/Saint Sri Kaleshwar (Jan 8, 1973-Mar 15, 2012).Lora received numerous initiations in the Shakti Energy Channels, including advanced yogas through the practice of mantra and yantra, and Mother Divine darshans.
